00:00:23.257 --> 00:00:26.093 position:24% line:89% align:start
[firework sparking]

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:40.440 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's been a while,

00:00:41.174 --> 00:00:42.175 position:13% line:89% align:start
since we all met like this.

00:00:42.276 --> 00:00:44.044 position:38% line:89% align:start
I know.

00:00:44.846 --> 00:00:46.213 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sorry we were late.

00:00:46.313 --> 00:00:47.080 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's okay.

00:00:48.181 --> 00:00:50.384 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm just glad you could come.

00:00:50.484 --> 00:00:53.220 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.522 position:41% line:89% align:start
Man...

00:00:54.622 --> 00:00:55.557 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's summer already.

00:00:57.559 --> 00:01:00.662 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:01:00.762 --> 00:01:01.696 position:33% line:89% align:start
Went by fast.

00:01:02.830 --> 00:01:05.365 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:01:05.465 --> 00:01:06.433 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ayane.

00:01:07.234 --> 00:01:09.704 position:27% line:5% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:23.785 position:24% line:89% align:start
[shop bell tinkles]

00:01:23.885 --> 00:01:25.185 position:38% line:89% align:start
You Aoi?

00:01:25.285 --> 00:01:27.187 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ah! Yeah.

00:01:27.287 --> 00:01:28.388 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's nice to meet you.

00:01:28.488 --> 00:01:30.390 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm Tomoya Sugisaki.

00:01:30.490 --> 00:01:31.659 position:33% line:89% align:start
How are you?

00:01:31.759 --> 00:01:33.393 position:21% line:83% align:start
- [shop bell tinkles]
- You guys are early.

00:01:34.662 --> 00:01:36.163 position:21% line:89% align:start
By like five minutes.

00:01:37.599 --> 00:01:39.099 position:35% line:89% align:start
Name's Ryo.

00:01:39.199 --> 00:01:40.300 position:19% line:89% align:start
Nice to meet you guys.

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.603 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:01:41.703 --> 00:01:43.303 position:13% line:89% align:start
So, we are all here, then.

00:01:44.839 --> 00:01:46.574 position:19% line:89% align:start
Uh, may as well start.

00:01:47.709 --> 00:01:48.743 position:33% line:89% align:start
[bell dings]

00:01:48.843 --> 00:01:50.845 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:01:50.945 --> 00:01:52.446 position:24% line:89% align:start
First things first.

00:01:52.547 --> 00:01:54.882 position:24% line:83% align:start
Okay, we decided to
meet today for one goal:

00:01:54.983 --> 00:01:56.416 position:10% line:83% align:start
to see if we can make contact
with the summer ghost.

00:01:58.418 --> 00:01:59.687 position:19% line:89% align:start
For the last two years,

00:01:59.787 --> 00:02:01.421 position:7% line:89% align:start
there have been sightings here

00:02:01.522 --> 00:02:02.690 position:24% line:89% align:start
during the summer.

00:02:02.790 --> 00:02:05.125 position:21% line:83% align:start
They say she appears
when there's fireworks.

00:02:05.225 --> 00:02:07.227 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [Aoi] <i>Fireworks?</i>
- [Ryo] <i>Yeah.</i>

00:02:07.327 --> 00:02:08.395 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Everyone who saw</i>
 <i>her had lit some.</i>

00:02:08.495 --> 00:02:09.463 position:27% line:89% align:start
[register dings]

00:02:09.564 --> 00:02:10.898 position:33% line:89% align:start
[pen clicks]

00:02:10.999 --> 00:02:12.734 position:24% line:83% align:start
Based on accounts,
she's about 20 years old.

00:02:12.834 --> 00:02:16.269 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's got long hair
and wears dark clothes.

00:02:16.370 --> 00:02:17.672 position:21% line:89% align:start
So if I had to guess,

00:02:17.772 --> 00:02:19.239 position:10% line:89% align:start
she probably looks like this.

00:02:19.339 --> 00:02:19.907 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're good.

00:02:21.341 --> 00:02:22.710 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:02:22.810 --> 00:02:24.444 position:30% line:83% align:start
You know, she's
actually quite pretty.

00:02:24.545 --> 00:02:25.680 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya chuckles]

00:02:25.780 --> 00:02:28.348 position:21% line:83% align:start
Now, according to the
rumors going around,

00:02:28.448 --> 00:02:29.751 position:19% line:89% align:start
she committed suicide.

00:02:30.752 --> 00:02:33.521 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:02:33.621 --> 00:02:34.589 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:02:35.957 --> 00:02:38.760 position:30% line:83% align:start
- What's wrong?
- Uh, it's nothing.

00:02:38.860 --> 00:02:40.460 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now that I think about it,

00:02:40.561 --> 00:02:41.696 position:24% line:89% align:start
aren't ghosts like,

00:02:41.796 --> 00:02:43.430 position:33% line:89% align:start
well, scary?

00:02:43.531 --> 00:02:45.399 position:33% line:83% align:start
You only just
thought of that now?

00:02:45.499 --> 00:02:46.668 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fine.

00:02:47.234 --> 00:02:48.836 position:19% line:83% align:start
- We're going, though.
- No!

00:02:48.936 --> 00:02:50.605 position:19% line:83% align:start
No, wait! I didn't mean
I didn't want to go!

00:02:50.705 --> 00:02:52.272 position:33% line:89% align:start
Wait for me!

00:02:52.372 --> 00:02:54.542 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just pointing out it
might get scary is all.

00:02:54.642 --> 00:02:56.511 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, so, uh, Tomoya,

00:02:56.611 --> 00:02:58.713 position:21% line:83% align:start
what made you want to
seek out the summer ghost?

00:02:58.946 --> 00:03:00.548 position:21% line:89% align:start
I was just wondering,

00:03:00.648 --> 00:03:02.449 position:13% line:83% align:start
since you were the one who
sent out the initial email.

00:03:02.550 --> 00:03:04.719 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hmm. It's a secret.

00:03:04.819 --> 00:03:06.521 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Aoi] What? Seriously?

00:03:06.621 --> 00:03:08.523 position:24% line:89% align:start
[laughs] You tease.

00:03:08.623 --> 00:03:11.258 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:03:12.794 --> 00:03:14.428 position:38% line:5% align:start
Sugisaki.

00:03:15.395 --> 00:03:17.665 position:35% line:5% align:start
A, A, A, A.

00:03:19.600 --> 00:03:20.635 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:03:21.636 --> 00:03:23.336 position:19% line:83% align:start
Grades are, of course,
not a problem for you.

00:03:23.437 --> 00:03:26.440 position:16% line:83% align:start
I wish my other students
were more like you.

00:03:26.541 --> 00:03:27.575 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:03:27.675 --> 00:03:29.242 position:30% line:89% align:start
[teacher sighs]

00:03:29.342 --> 00:03:30.277 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey.

00:03:30.377 --> 00:03:31.846 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes?

00:03:31.946 --> 00:03:32.714 position:24% line:89% align:start
[bottle pops open]

00:03:33.981 --> 00:03:35.850 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm counting on you.

00:03:35.950 --> 00:03:36.718 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya chuckles]

00:03:39.687 --> 00:03:42.456 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:00.440 position:30% line:83% align:start
- [Ryo] Tomoya.
- Uh, huh?

00:04:01.576 --> 00:04:04.011 position:27% line:83% align:start
What's with that
look? [chuckles]

00:04:04.112 --> 00:04:05.378 position:35% line:89% align:start
We're here.

00:04:05.479 --> 00:04:06.413 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya gasps]

00:04:08.082 --> 00:04:10.785 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:04:15.523 --> 00:04:16.557 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:04:17.658 --> 00:04:20.293 position:33% line:5% align:start
- It's huge.
- Yeah, it used to be
an airport.

00:04:20.762 --> 00:04:22.864 position:16% line:5% align:start
- No one flew out of it,
so they shut it down--
- [Ryo] Hey!

00:04:22.964 --> 00:04:23.965 position:44% line:83% align:start
- Oh!
- Huh?

00:04:24.065 --> 00:04:25.633 position:19% line:89% align:start
We gonna do this thing?

00:04:25.733 --> 00:04:28.468 position:24% line:89% align:start
[firework sparking]

00:04:32.073 --> 00:04:33.641 position:10% line:89% align:start
Do you think that it's real?

00:04:33.741 --> 00:04:35.576 position:21% line:83% align:start
Like, does the summer
ghost actually exist?

00:04:35.676 --> 00:04:37.011 position:33% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:04:37.111 --> 00:04:40.515 position:16% line:83% align:start
But people say fireworks
appease the spirits.

00:04:42.116 --> 00:04:43.416 position:19% line:89% align:start
I hope it reaches her.

00:04:44.952 --> 00:04:47.688 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:04:47.789 --> 00:04:50.625 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:04:52.459 --> 00:04:53.728 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Ryo] <i>I don't</i>
 <i>think she's coming</i>

00:04:53.828 --> 00:04:55.062 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Aoi] <i>But we lit so many.</i>

00:04:56.631 --> 00:04:58.465 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Ryo] <i>Well, this</i>
 <i>is the last one.</i>

00:04:58.566 --> 00:04:59.767 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>- You can have it.</i>
- [Aoi] <i>Thanks.</i>

00:05:05.873 --> 00:05:08.308 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:05:08.408 --> 00:05:10.578 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
 <i>Tomoya, you know,</i>

00:05:10.678 --> 00:05:13.380 position:24% line:83% align:start
I actually believed
in ghosts and stuff.

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:15.348 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Too bad they don't exist.</i>

00:05:16.383 --> 00:05:19.419 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>That said, this was the most</i>
 <i>fun I've had in a long time.</i>

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:21.488 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm really glad</i>
 <i>I met you guys.</i>

00:05:21.589 --> 00:05:22.623 position:24% line:89% align:start
So thanks for that.

00:05:22.723 --> 00:05:25.392 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:05:29.530 --> 00:05:31.966 position:24% line:89% align:start
[firework sparking]

00:05:32.066 --> 00:05:33.634 position:35% line:83% align:start
- [Aoi] Ah!
- Ah!

00:05:33.734 --> 00:05:34.702 position:38% line:89% align:start
The heck?

00:05:34.936 --> 00:05:35.970 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Aoi] What just happened?

00:05:37.839 --> 00:05:38.706 position:24% line:89% align:start
I think she's here.

00:05:40.007 --> 00:05:40.842 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:05:42.543 --> 00:05:44.411 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:05:44.512 --> 00:05:45.478 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:05:45.580 --> 00:05:46.346 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:05:47.882 --> 00:05:50.618 position:24% line:83% align:start
Excuse me, are you
the summer ghost?

00:05:50.718 --> 00:05:51.652 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that's me.

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:55.056 position:19% line:89% align:start
So what is it you want

00:05:55.156 --> 00:05:56.691 position:21% line:89% align:start
from someone like me?

00:05:56.791 --> 00:05:57.959 position:24% line:89% align:start
Someone who's dead.

00:05:58.059 --> 00:06:00.027 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Aoi gasps]

00:06:03.197 --> 00:06:06.534 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tapping floor]

00:06:06.634 --> 00:06:07.668 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Aoi sighs]

00:06:07.768 --> 00:06:10.838 position:24% line:89% align:start
[locker door slams]

00:06:10.938 --> 00:06:13.875 position:21% line:89% align:start
[students chattering]

00:06:18.546 --> 00:06:19.814 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:06:19.914 --> 00:06:22.550 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:06:23.851 --> 00:06:25.485 position:24% line:83% align:start
- [water splashing]
- Ah!

00:06:25.586 --> 00:06:26.721 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Student laughing] Nice aim!

00:06:26.821 --> 00:06:28.388 position:30% line:83% align:start
Yeah, she looks
like a drowned rat.

00:06:31.525 --> 00:06:32.860 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:35.730 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:06:35.830 --> 00:06:37.632 position:38% line:89% align:start
Get down!

00:06:37.732 --> 00:06:39.033 position:33% line:77% align:start
- What do you
think you're doing?
- Let go of me!

00:06:39.133 --> 00:06:40.501 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stop it!

00:06:41.569 --> 00:06:42.069 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Woman] <i>She only</i>
 <i>just returned to school</i>

00:06:42.870 --> 00:06:43.771 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>and there's another incident?</i>

00:06:45.072 --> 00:06:46.707 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Man] <i>Makes me think that</i>
 <i>she's part of the problem.</i>

00:06:46.807 --> 00:06:48.943 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Aoi crying]

00:06:54.615 --> 00:06:56.751 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Aoi] <i>Are there</i>
 <i>still cliques and stuff</i>

00:06:56.851 --> 00:06:57.919 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>when you're, like, a ghost?</i>

00:06:59.620 --> 00:07:01.856 position:38% line:89% align:start
Well, no.

00:07:01.956 --> 00:07:04.158 position:30% line:83% align:start
Because you're
basically on your own.

00:07:04.258 --> 00:07:05.026 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:07:06.694 --> 00:07:07.895 position:33% line:89% align:start
Good to know.

00:07:07.995 --> 00:07:09.429 position:21% line:89% align:start
That would be easier.

00:07:09.530 --> 00:07:11.198 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Summer Ghost] Yeah.
Being with other

00:07:11.299 --> 00:07:12.833 position:21% line:83% align:start
people definitely has
its pros and cons.

00:07:14.969 --> 00:07:16.504 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is something wrong?

00:07:16.604 --> 00:07:17.171 position:44% line:89% align:start
Look.

00:07:18.539 --> 00:07:19.707 position:16% line:89% align:start
The sparkler's still lit.

00:07:19.807 --> 00:07:21.441 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh.

00:07:21.542 --> 00:07:22.109 position:33% line:89% align:start
Kinda creepy.

00:07:24.145 --> 00:07:27.982 position:16% line:83% align:start
Hey, do you feel isolated
by your classmates?

00:07:28.082 --> 00:07:29.884 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is that the reason
you wanna die?

00:07:29.984 --> 00:07:31.484 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:07:31.585 --> 00:07:33.821 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not everyone is able
to see me, you know.

00:07:33.921 --> 00:07:38.059 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's only ones who've
been contemplating death.

00:07:40.161 --> 00:07:43.998 position:27% line:83% align:start
That means Tomoya
and Ryo have... [gasps]

00:07:46.968 --> 00:07:48.803 position:7% line:89% align:start
Now what about the two of you?

00:07:48.903 --> 00:07:50.470 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's your turn.

00:07:50.571 --> 00:07:51.639 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

00:07:51.739 --> 00:07:52.807 position:24% line:89% align:start
Miss Summer Ghost?

00:07:52.907 --> 00:07:53.841 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ayane Sato.

00:07:56.844 --> 00:07:57.678 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's my name.

00:07:59.113 --> 00:08:01.649 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're a ghost, right?

00:08:01.749 --> 00:08:03.617 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do we all become
one when we die?

00:08:03.718 --> 00:08:04.685 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows?

00:08:05.786 --> 00:08:07.655 position:10% line:89% align:start
What else do you want to ask?

00:08:07.755 --> 00:08:10.858 position:21% line:83% align:start
I want to know if the
world looks any different

00:08:10.958 --> 00:08:12.827 position:21% line:89% align:start
when you're a ghost.

00:08:12.927 --> 00:08:14.195 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Ayane sighs]

00:08:14.295 --> 00:08:15.062 position:27% line:89% align:start
I can't tell you.

00:08:16.697 --> 00:08:18.666 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's not something
you can explain.

00:08:20.034 --> 00:08:21.869 position:30% line:83% align:start
Only ghosts can
understand ghosts.

00:08:23.637 --> 00:08:25.840 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm afraid my time is up.

00:08:25.940 --> 00:08:28.209 position:24% line:83% align:start
Thanks so much for
our little chat.

00:08:28.309 --> 00:08:29.076 position:44% line:89% align:start
Boo!

00:08:30.311 --> 00:08:32.079 position:27% line:89% align:start
Take care, 'kay?

00:08:32.179 --> 00:08:34.515 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:08:34.615 --> 00:08:35.850 position:27% line:89% align:start
Take care, 'kay.

00:08:38.819 --> 00:08:40.654 position:19% line:89% align:start
Ghost really do exist.

00:08:40.755 --> 00:08:41.722 position:35% line:89% align:start
I knew it.

00:08:47.261 --> 00:08:48.562 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Doctor] That's basically it.

00:08:49.196 --> 00:08:50.831 position:21% line:83% align:start
.Make sure you inform
me of any changes.

00:08:50.931 --> 00:08:51.866 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I will.

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:54.001 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where are your parents?

00:08:54.101 --> 00:08:56.037 position:21% line:89% align:start
They're back at home.

00:08:56.137 --> 00:08:58.272 position:10% line:83% align:start
They'd only be a distraction
with all their crying.

00:08:59.640 --> 00:09:02.043 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:09:05.379 --> 00:09:06.680 position:30% line:77% align:start
- [boy groans]
- [Ryo] <i>Practicing hard,</i>
 <i>I see.</i>

00:09:06.781 --> 00:09:08.049 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:09:08.149 --> 00:09:09.050 position:27% line:89% align:start
Long time no see.

00:09:12.620 --> 00:09:14.922 position:16% line:83% align:start
You know, you never told
me why you quit basketball.

00:09:16.390 --> 00:09:17.725 position:21% line:89% align:start
I just felt like it.

00:09:17.825 --> 00:09:19.060 position:19% line:89% align:start
You just felt like it?

00:09:20.694 --> 00:09:22.296 position:27% line:89% align:start
'Cause I'm dying.

00:09:22.396 --> 00:09:23.564 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:09:23.664 --> 00:09:25.266 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:09:25.366 --> 00:09:27.568 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>I got about nine months left.</i>

00:09:27.668 --> 00:09:29.270 position:10% line:89% align:start
Won't get to see the Sakura.

00:09:29.370 --> 00:09:32.873 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ball bangs and bounces]

00:09:32.973 --> 00:09:34.341 position:7% line:89% align:start
Nah, I'm just messing with ya.

00:09:35.843 --> 00:09:37.011 position:30% line:89% align:start
Did you buy it?

00:09:37.111 --> 00:09:38.712 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:09:38.813 --> 00:09:39.580 position:44% line:89% align:start
Man!

00:09:40.781 --> 00:09:42.917 position:16% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't joke about
that kind of stuff.

00:09:43.017 --> 00:09:44.618 position:27% line:83% align:start
You really had me
there for a second.

00:09:48.856 --> 00:09:50.591 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:09:50.691 --> 00:09:52.126 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya sighs]

00:09:53.928 --> 00:09:56.097 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:10:04.038 --> 00:10:05.940 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Mother] <i>Tomoya, can</i>
 <i>you come here a</i> sec?

00:10:08.142 --> 00:10:10.678 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tomoya,</i>
 <i>I know you can hear me.</i>

00:10:10.778 --> 00:10:11.345 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:10:13.447 --> 00:10:16.283 position:21% line:83% align:start
The results from that
practice exam you took came in.

00:10:16.383 --> 00:10:19.120 position:24% line:83% align:start
You did pretty well
on the math part.

00:10:19.220 --> 00:10:20.287 position:7% line:89% align:start
Your essay questions need work.

00:10:21.722 --> 00:10:23.390 position:5% line:89% align:start
You have to answer the question.

00:10:23.491 --> 00:10:26.026 position:21% line:83% align:start
You can't just write
about how you're feeling.

00:10:26.127 --> 00:10:28.295 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>You understand what</i>
 <i>I'm saying, right?</i>

00:10:28.395 --> 00:10:31.098 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I don't know why you're</i>
 <i>having such trouble with this.</i>

00:10:31.198 --> 00:10:33.767 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:10:40.074 --> 00:10:41.642 position:35% line:5% align:start
[Aoi] <i>What?</i>

00:10:41.742 --> 00:10:42.643 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>You have cram school</i>
 <i>on Sundays, too?</i>

00:10:43.444 --> 00:10:45.679 position:33% line:83% align:start
Yeah, 'cause
exams are coming up.

00:10:45.779 --> 00:10:47.915 position:30% line:83% align:start
Wait, but mine
aren't 'til next year.

00:10:48.015 --> 00:10:49.783 position:21% line:83% align:start
Does that mean you're
older than me, Tomoya?

00:10:49.884 --> 00:10:52.119 position:38% line:83% align:start
Hold on.
So you're only a junior?

00:10:52.219 --> 00:10:54.655 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Aoi] <i>You're not, Ryo?</i>
 <i>I mean, uh...</i>

00:10:54.755 --> 00:10:56.924 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Ryo laughing] <i>Ryo's fine.</i>

00:10:57.024 --> 00:10:59.126 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:11:00.794 --> 00:11:01.829 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:11:03.764 --> 00:11:04.398 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:11:06.867 --> 00:11:07.701 position:24% line:5% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:11:15.976 --> 00:11:18.679 position:27% line:89% align:start
[mobile chiming]

00:11:19.980 --> 00:11:21.015 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Hello?
- Hello?

00:11:21.448 --> 00:11:22.850 position:24% line:89% align:start
Aoi? What changed?

00:11:23.317 --> 00:11:25.019 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Are you okay?
- Mm-hm.

00:11:25.119 --> 00:11:27.288 position:27% line:89% align:start
Nothing happened.

00:11:27.388 --> 00:11:29.089 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's just...

00:11:29.190 --> 00:11:31.358 position:27% line:83% align:start
Sometimes I can't
believe it was real.

00:11:31.458 --> 00:11:34.929 position:30% line:83% align:start
Just try not to
overthink it too much.

00:11:35.029 --> 00:11:36.964 position:21% line:83% align:start
I mean, what happened
wasn't exactly normal.

00:11:40.067 --> 00:11:42.036 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Tomoya?
- Sorry.

00:11:42.136 --> 00:11:44.171 position:13% line:89% align:start
I should probably hang up,

00:11:44.271 --> 00:11:45.873 position:19% line:89% align:start
'cause I'm almost home.

00:11:45.973 --> 00:11:47.041 position:41% line:89% align:start
Later.

00:11:47.141 --> 00:11:49.743 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:11:52.479 --> 00:11:53.814 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Ayane]
 <i>Hi, there.</i>

00:11:53.914 --> 00:11:54.481 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>So you came back.</i>

00:11:56.183 --> 00:11:57.785 position:19% line:89% align:start
Your face says it all.

00:11:57.885 --> 00:12:00.054 position:10% line:89% align:start
You just couldn't stay away.

00:12:00.821 --> 00:12:02.756 position:27% line:83% align:start
- I was curious.
- Hmm.

00:12:03.991 --> 00:12:05.192 position:35% line:89% align:start
Or greedy.

00:12:05.292 --> 00:12:08.062 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:12:08.162 --> 00:12:10.764 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey, Tomoya, why do
you think you're alive?

00:12:12.466 --> 00:12:14.735 position:30% line:83% align:start
What makes you
so sure I'm alive?

00:12:14.835 --> 00:12:16.003 position:30% line:83% align:start
- Do I look it?
- Only somewhat.

00:12:17.938 --> 00:12:19.306 position:33% line:89% align:start
The thing is,

00:12:19.406 --> 00:12:22.076 position:7% line:89% align:start
I don't really feel like I am.

00:12:22.176 --> 00:12:25.246 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's so bad sometimes I can't
even tell if I'm alive or not.

00:12:27.181 --> 00:12:29.383 position:16% line:83% align:start
[laughs] Well, that just
means your spirit's dead.

00:12:30.818 --> 00:12:32.019 position:21% line:89% align:start
Which isn't healthy.

00:12:32.119 --> 00:12:34.255 position:30% line:83% align:start
Pretty ironic,
coming from you.

00:12:34.355 --> 00:12:36.423 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, what are you
gonna do about it, then?

00:12:39.226 --> 00:12:40.227 position:19% line:89% align:start
I haven't decided yet.

00:12:42.296 --> 00:12:44.498 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's why I wanted to ask you.

00:12:44.599 --> 00:12:46.900 position:19% line:89% align:start
All of these feelings,

00:12:47.001 --> 00:12:50.237 position:19% line:83% align:start
the pain, do you still
have them as a ghost?

00:12:50.337 --> 00:12:53.207 position:21% line:89% align:start
Because if you don't,

00:12:53.307 --> 00:12:54.975 position:10% line:89% align:start
I might change my situation.

00:12:56.910 --> 00:12:57.545 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, I see.

00:12:59.847 --> 00:13:01.148 position:16% line:89% align:start
Wanna see what it's like?

00:13:01.248 --> 00:13:02.216 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:04.318 --> 00:13:06.320 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah, for a change of pace.

00:13:07.288 --> 00:13:08.322 position:27% line:89% align:start
Come fly with me.

00:13:09.490 --> 00:13:12.293 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whooshing]

00:13:12.393 --> 00:13:15.162 position:27% line:89% align:start
[whimsical music]

00:13:21.001 --> 00:13:22.436 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ready?

00:13:22.537 --> 00:13:23.804 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right.

00:13:23.904 --> 00:13:26.173 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hold on tight, okay?

00:13:26.273 --> 00:13:27.241 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:13:29.109 --> 00:13:31.345 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

00:13:38.118 --> 00:13:40.588 position:47% line:83% align:start
So?
How do you like it?

00:13:40.689 --> 00:13:42.222 position:30% line:83% align:start
With your body
back on the ground,

00:13:42.323 --> 00:13:43.457 position:19% line:89% align:start
your soul is free now.

00:13:47.294 --> 00:13:48.929 position:24% line:89% align:start
[quietly] Amazing.

00:13:49.897 --> 00:13:53.133 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:13:53.233 --> 00:13:55.836 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya screaming]

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:02.476 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whooshing]

00:14:02.577 --> 00:14:05.279 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashes]

00:14:10.050 --> 00:14:10.884 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:14:14.622 --> 00:14:17.424 position:7% line:89% align:start
Did I fall through the ground?

00:14:17.525 --> 00:14:20.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Ayane] [laughs] <i>Sorry!</i>
 <i>My bad.</i>

00:14:20.194 --> 00:14:21.629 position:10% line:89% align:start
I wanted it to be a surprise.

00:14:21.730 --> 00:14:23.598 position:24% line:83% align:start
So you could figure
it out on your own.

00:14:23.698 --> 00:14:25.866 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, it was a bad idea.

00:14:25.966 --> 00:14:27.569 position:33% line:89% align:start
I said sorry.

00:14:27.669 --> 00:14:30.237 position:21% line:83% align:start
Look, to make amends,
I'll teach you how to fly.

00:14:31.372 --> 00:14:33.107 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:14:33.207 --> 00:14:35.476 position:30% line:83% align:start
All you have to
do is wish for it.

00:14:35.577 --> 00:14:37.512 position:10% line:89% align:start
Deep, deep within your heart.

00:14:39.380 --> 00:14:41.516 position:19% line:83% align:start
Your soul will take you
wherever you desire.

00:14:43.016 --> 00:14:43.917 position:27% line:89% align:start
Now, picture it.

00:14:45.587 --> 00:14:47.421 position:5% line:89% align:start
Where is it that you want to go?

00:14:50.725 --> 00:14:53.394 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:14:57.732 --> 00:14:59.933 position:5% line:89% align:start
Does this mean you're an artist?

00:15:00.033 --> 00:15:01.235 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:15:01.335 --> 00:15:03.337 position:21% line:83% align:start
Though, I've stopped
pursuing it already.

00:15:03.437 --> 00:15:06.340 position:16% line:83% align:start
There are more important
things in the world, I'm told.

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:08.576 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is that why you've
become withdrawn?

00:15:08.676 --> 00:15:11.378 position:41% line:77% align:start
- What?
- Well, now that you have
this whole place to yourself,

00:15:11.478 --> 00:15:13.080 position:27% line:83% align:start
are you gonna let
it go to waste?

00:15:13.180 --> 00:15:14.481 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're a ghost now.

00:15:14.582 --> 00:15:15.916 position:5% line:89% align:start
They can't exactly kick you out.

00:15:17.084 --> 00:15:18.118 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:15:18.218 --> 00:15:20.555 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

00:15:43.745 --> 00:15:47.114 position:21% line:83% align:start
The city lights look
beautiful when you're a ghost.

00:15:47.214 --> 00:15:48.683 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, they sure do.

00:15:50.017 --> 00:15:52.554 position:10% line:83% align:start
And when you think about it,
since we can't see them flicker,

00:15:52.654 --> 00:15:55.088 position:21% line:83% align:start
they're actually even
brighter than this.

00:15:55.189 --> 00:15:56.256 position:35% line:89% align:start
Stop that.

00:15:56.356 --> 00:15:57.991 position:21% line:83% align:start
You know, you should
be thanking me

00:15:58.091 --> 00:15:59.426 position:10% line:89% align:start
instead of ruining the mood.

00:15:59.527 --> 00:16:01.028 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya laughs]
Sorry.

00:16:03.665 --> 00:16:07.167 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, uh, can I ask you
something personal?

00:16:07.267 --> 00:16:08.035 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Ayane] Shoot.

00:16:09.470 --> 00:16:11.639 position:16% line:83% align:start
I was wondering why'd you
decide to kill yourself?

00:16:14.408 --> 00:16:15.442 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tomoya...

00:16:17.044 --> 00:16:18.445 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're mistaken.

00:16:20.214 --> 00:16:21.583 position:13% line:89% align:start
I didn't take my own life.

00:16:22.784 --> 00:16:24.117 position:13% line:89% align:start
Want to know what happened?

00:16:25.820 --> 00:16:27.321 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why don't I tell you, then?

00:16:28.656 --> 00:16:29.490 position:33% line:89% align:start
The truth is

00:16:31.626 --> 00:16:32.459 position:33% line:89% align:start
I was killed.

00:16:36.463 --> 00:16:38.298 position:7% line:83% align:start
- [Tomoya] What is this place?
- [Ayane] My home.

00:16:39.466 --> 00:16:40.702 position:30% line:83% align:start
My mom lives by
herself here now.

00:16:42.336 --> 00:16:44.672 position:30% line:89% align:start
[somber music]

00:16:46.340 --> 00:16:49.409 position:13% line:83% align:start
That day, three years ago,
we had a really bad fight.

00:16:49.511 --> 00:16:50.477 position:30% line:89% align:start
[rain falling]

00:16:50.578 --> 00:16:52.446 position:27% line:89% align:start
And to be honest,

00:16:52.547 --> 00:16:55.082 position:21% line:83% align:start
it was over something
really minor.

00:16:55.182 --> 00:16:57.585 position:16% line:83% align:start
I was so upset I ended up
running out of the house

00:16:57.685 --> 00:16:58.987 position:13% line:89% align:start
in the middle of a typhoon.

00:16:59.119 --> 00:17:00.755 position:16% line:89% align:start
[vehicle crashes nearby]

00:17:00.855 --> 00:17:01.789 position:30% line:83% align:start
Right as I was
crossing the road,

00:17:03.190 --> 00:17:05.459 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was hit by a car who
was running a red light.

00:17:06.661 --> 00:17:08.195 position:10% line:89% align:start
Talk about dumb luck, right?

00:17:09.797 --> 00:17:13.500 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I was still alive,
just unconscious.

00:17:14.134 --> 00:17:15.302 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah.

00:17:15.402 --> 00:17:17.271 position:30% line:89% align:start
When I came to,

00:17:17.371 --> 00:17:19.707 position:21% line:83% align:start
I found myself locked
inside a cramped space.

00:17:19.807 --> 00:17:21.776 position:27% line:83% align:start
I have a feeling
it was a suitcase.

00:17:21.876 --> 00:17:23.176 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya] Why?

00:17:23.277 --> 00:17:24.546 position:27% line:83% align:start
Probably to cover
up the accident.

00:17:25.813 --> 00:17:27.615 position:30% line:83% align:start
The driver then
buried me somewhere.

00:17:28.550 --> 00:17:30.384 position:10% line:89% align:start
I was struggling to breathe.

00:17:30.484 --> 00:17:32.720 position:21% line:83% align:start
Then I heard a train
in the distance.

00:17:34.288 --> 00:17:35.790 position:33% line:89% align:start
Then nothing.

00:17:35.890 --> 00:17:37.559 position:16% line:89% align:start
That was my final memory.

00:17:39.827 --> 00:17:42.162 position:19% line:83% align:start
My mom's still waiting
for me to come home.

00:17:42.864 --> 00:17:45.098 position:21% line:83% align:start
Do you have any idea
where you were buried?

00:17:45.198 --> 00:17:47.669 position:27% line:83% align:start
I tried to figure
that out at first.

00:17:47.769 --> 00:17:49.436 position:5% line:89% align:start
But it wouldn't change anything.

00:17:52.272 --> 00:17:56.410 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh, man, there's so many
things I didn't get to do.

00:17:56.511 --> 00:17:58.846 position:7% line:89% align:start
Travel the world, fall in love.

00:17:58.947 --> 00:18:00.548 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm jealous of the
future ahead of you.

00:18:01.883 --> 00:18:04.519 position:47% line:83% align:start
Mm.
But you can still travel.

00:18:04.619 --> 00:18:06.453 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's more, you can
even do it for free.

00:18:06.554 --> 00:18:07.522 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Ayane]
 <i>Hey!</i>

00:18:08.523 --> 00:18:11.325 position:13% line:83% align:start
That was a tad insensitive.
You get a demerit.

00:18:13.393 --> 00:18:16.698 position:30% line:83% align:start
But I honestly
am jealous of you.

00:18:18.866 --> 00:18:21.401 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [Ayane] Tomoya.
- [Tomoya] Yes?

00:18:22.604 --> 00:18:25.272 position:30% line:83% align:start
Would you help
me find my body?

00:18:25.372 --> 00:18:26.708 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:18:26.808 --> 00:18:29.510 position:24% line:83% align:start
I feel like I could
find it if you helped me.

00:18:29.744 --> 00:18:32.412 position:24% line:83% align:start
The whole reason I
gave up looking for it

00:18:32.513 --> 00:18:35.783 position:13% line:83% align:start
was 'cause I couldn't touch
it, even if I found it.

00:18:36.918 --> 00:18:39.554 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:18:39.887 --> 00:18:42.890 position:27% line:89% align:start
[chuckles] Sorry.

00:18:42.991 --> 00:18:45.125 position:30% line:83% align:start
I made this all
about me in the end.

00:18:45.492 --> 00:18:47.427 position:7% line:89% align:start
You can forget I said anything.

00:18:48.328 --> 00:18:50.330 position:27% line:89% align:start
Take care, 'kay?

00:18:50.430 --> 00:18:52.900 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:19:01.542 --> 00:19:03.911 position:21% line:89% align:start
[students chattering]

00:19:04.012 --> 00:19:06.614 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Aoi sniffling]

00:19:10.752 --> 00:19:13.855 position:30% line:89% align:start
[water running]

00:19:13.955 --> 00:19:16.289 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:19:20.360 --> 00:19:23.330 position:21% line:89% align:start
[person claps nearby]

00:19:25.232 --> 00:19:27.602 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:19:30.738 --> 00:19:33.675 position:30% line:89% align:start
[car rumbling]

00:19:33.775 --> 00:19:35.777 position:27% line:83% align:start
I thought you had
cram school today.

00:19:37.612 --> 00:19:38.813 position:41% line:89% align:start
Get in.

00:19:40.815 --> 00:19:42.817 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's the second term already.

00:19:43.017 --> 00:19:44.819 position:24% line:83% align:start
I know you've been
out and about.

00:19:45.653 --> 00:19:46.854 position:24% line:89% align:start
You can't fool me.

00:19:47.387 --> 00:19:48.221 position:33% line:89% align:start
I've been...

00:19:48.856 --> 00:19:50.525 position:21% line:89% align:start
looking for a friend.

00:19:50.625 --> 00:19:53.795 position:13% line:83% align:start
A friend? Is a friend more
important than your own future?

00:19:54.428 --> 00:19:56.898 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'll be calling your cram school
to make sure you're going.

00:19:57.330 --> 00:19:58.733 position:27% line:83% align:start
You need to start
facing reality.

00:19:58.833 --> 00:19:59.967 position:44% line:83% align:start
- Ah!
- [car door slams]

00:20:00.068 --> 00:20:01.502 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, where do you
think you're going?

00:20:01.602 --> 00:20:02.804 position:19% line:89% align:start
Come back here, Tomoya!

00:20:02.904 --> 00:20:03.671 position:27% line:89% align:start
[register dings]

00:20:04.539 --> 00:20:05.573 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:20:08.275 --> 00:20:10.645 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:20:13.480 --> 00:20:14.682 position:38% line:89% align:start
Nothing.

00:20:14.782 --> 00:20:16.349 position:21% line:89% align:start
No luck today either.

00:20:18.553 --> 00:20:19.386 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:20:19.887 --> 00:20:20.988 position:38% line:89% align:start
What for?

00:20:21.089 --> 00:20:22.623 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's not your fault.

00:20:23.057 --> 00:20:24.992 position:24% line:83% align:start
Besides, these are
like dates for me.

00:20:27.394 --> 00:20:30.397 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm supposed to take my
entrance exams this year.

00:20:31.398 --> 00:20:32.834 position:21% line:89% align:start
Once I'm in college,

00:20:33.534 --> 00:20:35.803 position:19% line:83% align:start
I won't be able to come
back here very often.

00:20:37.404 --> 00:20:38.405 position:41% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:20:39.574 --> 00:20:41.843 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Ayane] <i>Then let's just</i>
 <i>stop looking for me.</i>

00:20:41.943 --> 00:20:42.910 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:20:44.178 --> 00:20:47.280 position:10% line:83% align:start
Summer's almost over anyway,
so it's kind of perfect timing.

00:20:47.481 --> 00:20:49.717 position:16% line:83% align:start
Hold on. We don't have to
give up looking--

00:20:49.817 --> 00:20:50.785 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's okay.

00:20:51.686 --> 00:20:53.020 position:24% line:83% align:start
I shouldn't bother
you anymore with it.

00:20:53.688 --> 00:20:54.956 position:21% line:89% align:start
Your time is limited.

00:20:55.056 --> 00:20:56.791 position:21% line:83% align:start
No need to waste any
more of it on me.

00:20:56.891 --> 00:20:57.992 position:38% line:89% align:start
No, wait.

00:20:58.092 --> 00:20:59.594 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's another demerit.

00:21:00.393 --> 00:21:02.764 position:21% line:83% align:start
Girls don't like men
who are too persistent.

00:21:03.731 --> 00:21:06.033 position:27% line:83% align:start
I said it's fine.
So it's fine.

00:21:06.634 --> 00:21:07.769 position:27% line:89% align:start
Why is that?

00:21:08.936 --> 00:21:11.371 position:10% line:83% align:start
Is it 'cause you don't think
you'll be here much longer?

00:21:11.471 --> 00:21:12.272 position:38% line:89% align:start
Perhaps.

00:21:13.674 --> 00:21:14.842 position:27% line:89% align:start
I think I get it.

00:21:15.810 --> 00:21:17.477 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll see you tomorrow at dusk.

00:21:18.780 --> 00:21:19.847 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please wait for me.

00:21:22.784 --> 00:21:24.585 position:16% line:89% align:start
Are you free to meet now?

00:21:26.020 --> 00:21:27.354 position:27% line:89% align:start
I need your help.

00:21:28.022 --> 00:21:30.357 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]
 <i>I want to find Ayane's body,</i>

00:21:30.858 --> 00:21:32.527 position:7% line:89% align:start
but I'll need the both of you.

00:21:33.728 --> 00:21:35.830 position:13% line:89% align:start
I knew this was about her.

00:21:36.429 --> 00:21:38.566 position:21% line:83% align:start
Let me guess, you've
been meeting up with her.

00:21:38.666 --> 00:21:39.600 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:21:39.934 --> 00:21:41.068 position:38% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:21:41.169 --> 00:21:41.969 position:21% line:89% align:start
Did you fall for her?

00:21:43.403 --> 00:21:44.038 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stop it.

00:21:45.673 --> 00:21:47.074 position:35% line:83% align:start
- Whatever.
- Huh?

00:21:47.608 --> 00:21:49.510 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Ryo] You can count me out.

00:21:49.610 --> 00:21:50.845 position:24% line:89% align:start
She killed herself.

00:21:50.945 --> 00:21:52.312 position:21% line:89% align:start
It serves her right.

00:21:52.412 --> 00:21:54.615 position:47% line:83% align:start
No.
She was murdered.

00:21:55.650 --> 00:21:57.051 position:16% line:89% align:start
This is important to me.

00:21:58.418 --> 00:22:00.688 position:13% line:89% align:start
Because if I don't do this,

00:22:00.788 --> 00:22:03.090 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll regret it for
the rest of my life.

00:22:03.191 --> 00:22:04.926 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Ryo] Oh, yeah?

00:22:05.026 --> 00:22:06.694 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, then I wish you luck.

00:22:07.061 --> 00:22:08.663 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Ryo.
- [Ryo] Don't.

00:22:08.763 --> 00:22:10.363 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Wait!
- I said don't!

00:22:11.933 --> 00:22:13.768 position:7% line:89% align:start
I don't want to hear it, 'kay?

00:22:13.868 --> 00:22:16.469 position:27% line:89% align:start
I can't take it.

00:22:16.571 --> 00:22:18.105 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's easy for you to
say stuff like that.

00:22:18.206 --> 00:22:19.941 position:27% line:83% align:start
'Cause you have a
rest of your life.

00:22:20.975 --> 00:22:22.610 position:30% line:89% align:start
Unlike others.

00:22:22.710 --> 00:22:24.612 position:33% line:83% align:start
- Unlike me.
- You mean?

00:22:24.712 --> 00:22:25.478 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ryo, wait!

00:22:28.850 --> 00:22:31.052 position:24% line:89% align:start
[shop bell tinkles]

00:22:31.152 --> 00:22:33.888 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:22:36.991 --> 00:22:39.694 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is something wrong?

00:22:39.794 --> 00:22:41.629 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Tomoya?
- No.

00:22:41.729 --> 00:22:43.130 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's fine.

00:22:43.231 --> 00:22:44.464 position:27% line:89% align:start
Today's the day.

00:22:44.565 --> 00:22:46.067 position:7% line:89% align:start
We're going to find your body.

00:22:46.167 --> 00:22:47.134 position:19% line:89% align:start
[crossing post blaring]

00:22:47.235 --> 00:22:50.370 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:22:50.470 --> 00:22:51.572 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait!

00:22:51.672 --> 00:22:52.472 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ooh!

00:22:52.573 --> 00:22:53.841 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ryo!

00:22:53.941 --> 00:22:56.677 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:23:02.950 --> 00:23:05.720 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Aoi panting]

00:23:05.820 --> 00:23:07.889 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Ryo!
- Stay away from me!

00:23:09.790 --> 00:23:11.525 position:21% line:89% align:start
Just leave me alone.

00:23:11.626 --> 00:23:13.928 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:23:15.129 --> 00:23:15.963 position:38% line:89% align:start
Damn it.

00:23:18.733 --> 00:23:22.570 position:7% line:83% align:start
You haven't quite mastered it,
so we can't go far, huh?

00:23:22.670 --> 00:23:24.171 position:41% line:83% align:start
Still.
I'm going to find you.

00:23:26.641 --> 00:23:27.474 position:41% line:89% align:start
Tomoya.

00:23:31.512 --> 00:23:33.446 position:16% line:89% align:start
I want to be left alone.

00:23:34.949 --> 00:23:36.017 position:16% line:89% align:start
I knew this would happen.

00:23:37.551 --> 00:23:38.920 position:7% line:89% align:start
I knew it'd make things worse.

00:23:41.055 --> 00:23:43.124 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm going to die anyway.

00:23:43.224 --> 00:23:44.792 position:7% line:89% align:start
So why bother with anyone else?

00:23:46.260 --> 00:23:47.828 position:5% line:89% align:start
Why did I have to meet you guys?

00:23:48.796 --> 00:23:50.497 position:44% line:89% align:start
Why?

00:23:50.598 --> 00:23:51.165 position:41% line:89% align:start
Why me?

00:23:51.899 --> 00:23:53.668 position:7% line:89% align:start
Nothing ever goes right for me.

00:23:55.636 --> 00:23:57.138 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ryo.

00:23:57.238 --> 00:24:00.508 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't know if it's really
my place to weigh in, but...

00:24:00.608 --> 00:24:01.175 position:35% line:89% align:start
truth is...

00:24:03.110 --> 00:24:05.445 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm being bullied at school.</i>

00:24:05.546 --> 00:24:07.715 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's pretty bad.</i>

00:24:07.815 --> 00:24:11.185 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's caused me so much</i>
 <i>pain for such a long time.</i>

00:24:11.285 --> 00:24:13.554 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I was so hopeless.</i>

00:24:13.654 --> 00:24:15.189 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I didn't even know</i>
 <i>why I was alive.</i>

00:24:16.257 --> 00:24:20.795 position:27% line:83% align:start
And so I went out
searching for answers

00:24:20.895 --> 00:24:22.229 position:13% line:89% align:start
and tried to find a ghost.

00:24:23.764 --> 00:24:27.001 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I know my situation</i>
 <i>doesn't compare to yours</i>

00:24:27.101 --> 00:24:30.738 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and I'm sure that Tomoya</i>
 <i>has his own troubles, too.</i>

00:24:30.838 --> 00:24:32.974 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>But I believe that</i>
 <i>there has to be a reason</i>

00:24:33.074 --> 00:24:34.075 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>why the three of us met.</i>

00:24:35.276 --> 00:24:36.577 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:24:36.677 --> 00:24:37.645 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bag rustling]

00:24:37.745 --> 00:24:38.579 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:24:38.679 --> 00:24:39.647 position:41% line:89% align:start
Oh, no!

00:24:42.216 --> 00:24:43.751 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ayane!

00:24:43.851 --> 00:24:45.052 position:27% line:89% align:start
Can you hear me?

00:24:45.152 --> 00:24:46.454 position:21% line:89% align:start
Are you still around?

00:24:48.089 --> 00:24:51.092 position:30% line:89% align:start
[somber music]

00:24:51.192 --> 00:24:52.927 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Ryo] <i>You ran outta sparklers?</i>

00:24:53.027 --> 00:24:54.595 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>- Amateur move.</i>
- Huh?

00:24:54.695 --> 00:24:55.663 position:19% line:89% align:start
[plastic bag rustling]

00:24:56.764 --> 00:24:58.099 position:19% line:83% align:start
You know, you're never
gonna find her at that rate.

00:24:58.199 --> 00:25:00.668 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:25:02.937 --> 00:25:03.971 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:25:04.905 --> 00:25:06.841 position:5% line:89% align:start
I was caught up in my own stuff.

00:25:06.941 --> 00:25:09.143 position:19% line:89% align:start
I should have noticed.

00:25:09.243 --> 00:25:10.878 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I never considered</i>
 <i>your feelings.</i>

00:25:10.978 --> 00:25:13.014 position:16% line:83% align:start
You know, I really can't
stand people like you.

00:25:15.249 --> 00:25:17.651 position:27% line:83% align:start
You always think
you know everything

00:25:17.752 --> 00:25:19.754 position:19% line:83% align:start
and so you always think
you have it the worst.

00:25:21.122 --> 00:25:22.757 position:33% line:89% align:start
[bag rustles]

00:25:22.857 --> 00:25:23.624 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'll help, though.

00:25:24.825 --> 00:25:26.761 position:24% line:89% align:start
You can thank Aoi.

00:25:26.861 --> 00:25:28.629 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Huh?
- Thanks, Ryo.

00:25:31.065 --> 00:25:32.099 position:30% line:89% align:start
Come on, then.

00:25:36.037 --> 00:25:37.705 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya] <i>This means a lot.</i>

00:25:37.805 --> 00:25:40.307 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:25:53.988 --> 00:25:57.058 position:21% line:89% align:start
[inaudible dialogue]

00:26:02.663 --> 00:26:04.799 position:30% line:83% align:start
My body, do you
think we'll find it?

00:26:04.899 --> 00:26:06.667 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, of course.

00:26:06.767 --> 00:26:07.668 position:19% line:89% align:start
There's four of us now.

00:26:09.970 --> 00:26:13.274 position:16% line:83% align:start
I didn't realize that you
would search this hard for me.

00:26:13.374 --> 00:26:16.110 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm so grateful for
the three of you.

00:26:16.210 --> 00:26:19.180 position:19% line:83% align:start
Nothing is better than
having good friends.

00:26:19.280 --> 00:26:20.047 position:24% line:89% align:start
Take care of them.

00:26:21.916 --> 00:26:23.184 position:47% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:26:23.284 --> 00:26:24.585 position:30% line:83% align:start
- [Aoi] <i>Tomoya!</i>
- Ah!

00:26:24.952 --> 00:26:26.353 position:27% line:89% align:start
What is it? Aoi!

00:26:26.454 --> 00:26:27.788 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Aoi]
 <i>Follow me, quickly!</i>

00:26:27.888 --> 00:26:29.090 position:33% line:89% align:start
The suitcase!

00:26:29.190 --> 00:26:30.157 position:21% line:89% align:start
I may have found it.

00:26:31.725 --> 00:26:34.128 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water gurgling]

00:26:35.930 --> 00:26:36.964 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's over there.

00:26:37.898 --> 00:26:39.366 position:24% line:89% align:start
'Kay. I'll go look.

00:26:42.103 --> 00:26:43.704 position:30% line:83% align:start
I wonder what's
going to happen.

00:26:43.804 --> 00:26:45.005 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:26:45.106 --> 00:26:46.373 position:7% line:89% align:start
Like, will her ghost disappear

00:26:46.474 --> 00:26:48.175 position:24% line:83% align:start
when she's reunited
with her body?

00:26:49.310 --> 00:26:50.878 position:24% line:89% align:start
I feel kind of sad.

00:26:52.146 --> 00:26:53.280 position:27% line:89% align:start
[whimsical music]

00:26:53.380 --> 00:26:54.148 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:26:55.416 --> 00:26:57.184 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is the correct suitcase.

00:26:57.284 --> 00:26:58.352 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right!

00:26:58.452 --> 00:26:59.820 position:35% line:83% align:start
- Let's go!
- Mm!

00:27:01.422 --> 00:27:03.757 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm so relieved.

00:27:03.858 --> 00:27:06.127 position:16% line:83% align:start
I hope this gives my mom
the closure she needs.

00:27:06.227 --> 00:27:07.194 position:38% line:89% align:start
So then,

00:27:08.295 --> 00:27:10.064 position:5% line:89% align:start
does this mean you'll disappear?

00:27:10.164 --> 00:27:11.132 position:38% line:89% align:start
Probably.

00:27:12.233 --> 00:27:14.068 position:30% line:89% align:start
But no regrets.

00:27:14.168 --> 00:27:15.836 position:10% line:89% align:start
'Cause it was fun in the end.

00:27:15.936 --> 00:27:18.405 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water dripping]

00:27:20.908 --> 00:27:22.042 position:35% line:89% align:start
And Tomoya?

00:27:22.143 --> 00:27:24.311 position:13% line:89% align:start
Good luck with everything.

00:27:24.411 --> 00:27:25.179 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:27:27.848 --> 00:27:31.051 position:19% line:83% align:start
Because you still have
a life left to live.

00:27:32.019 --> 00:27:33.854 position:24% line:89% align:start
[insects trilling]

00:27:33.954 --> 00:27:35.356 position:27% line:89% align:start
Ah, you're awake.

00:27:35.456 --> 00:27:36.824 position:24% line:83% align:start
Okay then, what are
you waiting for?

00:27:37.158 --> 00:27:38.359 position:35% line:83% align:start
- Hurry up.
- Yeah.

00:27:39.026 --> 00:27:40.327 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm worried.

00:27:40.427 --> 00:27:43.764 position:19% line:83% align:start
You seem to enjoy being
a ghost a bit too much.

00:27:43.864 --> 00:27:47.301 position:10% line:83% align:start
For example, you don't think
dying would be that bad.

00:27:47.968 --> 00:27:49.703 position:33% line:83% align:start
- Am I right?
- Huh?

00:27:49.937 --> 00:27:51.906 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Ayane laughs]

00:27:52.006 --> 00:27:52.773 position:41% line:89% align:start
Tomoya.

00:27:55.009 --> 00:27:56.043 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:27:57.144 --> 00:27:58.245 position:21% line:89% align:start
I was rather selfish.

00:27:58.345 --> 00:28:00.714 position:33% line:89% align:start
[all panting]

00:28:02.983 --> 00:28:04.418 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Ryo!
- I'm okay.

00:28:04.519 --> 00:28:05.920 position:33% line:89% align:start
Go on ahead.

00:28:06.020 --> 00:28:07.154 position:13% line:89% align:start
Ayane's waited long enough.

00:28:08.455 --> 00:28:11.025 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:28:11.125 --> 00:28:13.427 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both panting]

00:28:15.329 --> 00:28:17.364 position:27% line:83% align:start
- It's in there.
- Yeah.

00:28:17.464 --> 00:28:19.233 position:38% line:89% align:start
But look!

00:28:19.333 --> 00:28:21.702 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Ayane] You had your own
problems to deal with,

00:28:21.802 --> 00:28:23.237 position:24% line:83% align:start
but I still dragged
you around everywhere.

00:28:24.805 --> 00:28:27.208 position:27% line:83% align:start
And now I'm just
leaving you behind.

00:28:30.211 --> 00:28:31.979 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't be sad for me.

00:28:32.079 --> 00:28:32.846 position:41% line:89% align:start
Listen,

00:28:34.048 --> 00:28:35.249 position:21% line:89% align:start
I wanted to find you.

00:28:36.083 --> 00:28:37.184 position:27% line:89% align:start
It was my choice.

00:28:38.520 --> 00:28:39.920 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Ayane chuckles]

00:28:41.021 --> 00:28:41.855 position:35% line:89% align:start
Okay, then.

00:28:42.823 --> 00:28:44.225 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:28:45.259 --> 00:28:46.894 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm sure you'll figure it out.

00:28:48.295 --> 00:28:51.031 position:10% line:89% align:start
Dying is part of your future,

00:28:51.131 --> 00:28:52.299 position:27% line:89% align:start
but it's my past.

00:28:53.635 --> 00:28:56.070 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>It lies exactly in the</i>
 <i>middle between the two of us.</i>

00:28:56.170 --> 00:28:58.872 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:29:03.244 --> 00:29:04.278 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:29:05.379 --> 00:29:07.248 position:41% line:83% align:start
- Aoi?
- You can do it!

00:29:07.348 --> 00:29:08.315 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't give up!

00:29:09.450 --> 00:29:10.284 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:29:12.286 --> 00:29:15.189 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:29:26.568 --> 00:29:28.235 position:41% line:89% align:start
[ding]

00:29:33.841 --> 00:29:35.175 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:29:35.276 --> 00:29:36.910 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

00:29:37.011 --> 00:29:38.245 position:41% line:89% align:start
Tomoya!

00:29:38.345 --> 00:29:39.313 position:41% line:89% align:start
Tomoya!

00:29:44.619 --> 00:29:47.955 position:10% line:83% align:start
You've been wandering around
as a spirit for a long time.

00:29:48.055 --> 00:29:49.056 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's why you're here.

00:29:51.492 --> 00:29:55.029 position:21% line:83% align:start
This is death, where
there's nothing.

00:29:55.129 --> 00:29:58.299 position:16% line:83% align:start
However, it's also where
every bit of you gathers.

00:30:01.503 --> 00:30:03.270 position:16% line:89% align:start
You just have to burn it.

00:30:03.370 --> 00:30:06.040 position:16% line:83% align:start
Then you can say goodbye
to the rest of the world.

00:30:06.140 --> 00:30:08.475 position:30% line:89% align:start
[match strikes]

00:30:08.576 --> 00:30:11.078 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:30:12.614 --> 00:30:14.915 position:19% line:89% align:start
But I shouldn't, right?

00:30:15.983 --> 00:30:17.051 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:30:17.151 --> 00:30:18.819 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's with that look?

00:30:18.919 --> 00:30:19.486 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:30:21.055 --> 00:30:22.856 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on.

00:30:22.956 --> 00:30:24.425 position:16% line:89% align:start
What do you really want?

00:30:25.527 --> 00:30:29.063 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:30:29.163 --> 00:30:31.865 position:24% line:89% align:start
[firework sparking]

00:30:37.371 --> 00:30:39.006 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Ryo] <i>Tomoya!</i>

00:30:39.106 --> 00:30:41.008 position:27% line:83% align:start
- [Tomoya gasps]
- [Ryo] <i>What are you doing?</i>

00:30:41.108 --> 00:30:42.544 position:30% line:89% align:start
Snap out of it!

00:30:42.644 --> 00:30:44.478 position:33% line:77% align:start
- Ryo, stop.
