who wanted to do this!

00:30:44.579 --> 00:30:46.280 position:27% line:83% align:start
So now it's time
to follow through.

00:30:47.448 --> 00:30:49.016 position:16% line:89% align:start
If you give up right now,

00:30:50.351 --> 00:30:51.385 position:16% line:89% align:start
