00:30:53.253 --> 00:30:54.288 position:38% line:89% align:start
I can't.

00:30:55.356 --> 00:30:56.423 position:24% line:89% align:start
I have to go back.

00:30:56.524 --> 00:30:57.491 position:38% line:89% align:start
What for?

00:30:57.592 --> 00:31:00.194 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whooshing]

00:31:01.328 --> 00:31:02.429 position:30% line:89% align:start
What is there?

00:31:04.131 --> 00:31:07.901 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why cling to something that
has only brought you pain?

00:31:08.001 --> 00:31:10.404 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:31:12.373 --> 00:31:13.440 position:33% line:89% align:start
Why go back?

00:31:13.541 --> 00:31:14.509 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:31:15.677 --> 00:31:18.613 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:31:18.713 --> 00:31:21.649 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah, life's been painful.

00:31:23.317 --> 00:31:24.985 position:19% line:89% align:start
But it's not over yet!

00:31:26.153 --> 00:31:27.454 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>And it's not all bad.</i>

00:31:27.555 --> 00:31:30.057 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>For example, Ryo and Aoi.</i>

00:31:30.157 --> 00:31:32.126 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I learned that if I</i>
 <i>put myself out there,</i>

00:31:32.226 --> 00:31:33.427 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can meet people like them.</i>

00:31:34.696 --> 00:31:36.263 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're not Ayane, you're me.

00:31:37.364 --> 00:31:39.900 position:7% line:89% align:start
Searching for a reason to die!

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:43.070 position:21% line:83% align:start
But I have to go back
so I can find Ayane.

00:31:45.205 --> 00:31:46.039 position:30% line:89% align:start
Everyone dies.

00:31:47.374 --> 00:31:48.676 position:24% line:89% align:start
But do we all live?

00:31:50.512 --> 00:31:52.212 position:35% line:89% align:start
I know now.

00:31:52.312 --> 00:31:54.616 position:19% line:83% align:start
There's so much to life
I still don't understand.

00:31:56.316 --> 00:31:58.620 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:32:03.558 --> 00:32:07.961 position:13% line:89% align:start
[firework sparking gently]

00:32:08.061 --> 00:32:10.197 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:32:10.297 --> 00:32:11.699 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya grunts]
[ding]

00:32:17.104 --> 00:32:18.972 position:38% line:83% align:start
- Tomoya!
- Tomoya!

00:32:19.072 --> 00:32:21.408 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:32:38.358 --> 00:32:39.561 position:24% line:89% align:start
[zipper unzipping]

00:32:42.129 --> 00:32:43.497 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah.

