[gentle piano music]

00:32:49.303 --> 00:32:50.505 position:38% line:89% align:start
Finally.

00:32:52.774 --> 00:32:56.043 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya crying quietly]

00:33:03.685 --> 00:33:05.620 position:33% line:89% align:start
You found me.

00:33:05.720 --> 00:33:06.688 position:30% line:89% align:start
Now I can rest.

00:33:07.689 --> 00:33:10.324 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:33:19.667 --> 00:33:21.201 position:16% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping outside]

00:33:21.301 --> 00:33:23.303 position:27% line:89% align:start
[doorbell chimes]

00:33:23.403 --> 00:33:24.371 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes?

00:33:27.675 --> 00:33:29.343 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:33:29.443 --> 00:33:30.377 position:30% line:89% align:start
[object clinks]

00:33:30.477 --> 00:33:31.445 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:33:33.146 --> 00:33:35.517 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:33:37.351 --> 00:33:38.385 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ayane?

00:33:39.621 --> 00:33:42.189 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:34:06.848 --> 00:34:09.651 position:24% line:89% align:start
[firework sparking]

00:34:21.228 --> 00:34:23.698 position:16% line:89% align:start
Man, it's summer already.

00:34:28.302 --> 00:34:29.369 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:34:29.469 --> 00:34:30.672 position:10% line:89% align:start
How have the two of you been?

00:34:31.639 --> 00:34:32.607 position:16% line:89% align:start
I hope you're both good.

00:34:35.643 --> 00:34:36.678 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hm.

00:34:38.513 --> 00:34:39.547 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hanging in there.

00:34:40.782 --> 00:34:44.284 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

00:34:44.384 --> 00:34:45.753 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] <i>Choosing to live how</i>
 <i>you want is...</i>

00:34:46.253 --> 00:34:47.755 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>harder than I</i>
 <i>would have thought.</i>

00:34:48.856 --> 00:34:50.157 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yeah, same.

00:34:52.694 --> 00:34:54.328 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Things haven't</i>
 <i>really gotten better.</i>

00:34:55.429 --> 00:34:57.331 position:27% line:89% align:start
[bully laughing]

00:34:57.431 --> 00:35:00.668 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water dripping]

00:35:00.768 --> 00:35:02.369 position:10% line:89% align:start
Ugh, what is wrong with you?

00:35:02.469 --> 00:35:04.672 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why do you insist on acting
like a bunch of little brats?

00:35:04.772 --> 00:35:06.608 position:30% line:83% align:start
But who knows?
Maybe things will change.

00:35:09.544 --> 00:35:11.579 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] <i>Sometimes I feel</i>
 <i>like it would've been easier</i>

00:35:11.679 --> 00:35:13.347 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>to just do as I'm told.</i>

00:35:14.849 --> 00:35:15.683 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>But you know what?</i>

00:35:17.451 --> 00:35:18.118 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm okay with it.</i>

00:35:19.854 --> 00:35:21.388 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Because when I think about</i>

00:35:21.488 --> 00:35:23.658 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>how everything is</i>
 <i>going to end someday,</i>

00:35:25.258 --> 00:35:26.761 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm not afraid of</i>
 <i>anything anymore.</i>

00:35:28.930 --> 00:35:32.165 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's why I'm going</i>
 <i>to go down my own path.</i>

00:35:36.203 --> 00:35:36.838 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:35:37.872 --> 00:35:38.706 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's good to hear.

00:35:40.541 --> 00:35:41.576 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:35:43.578 --> 00:35:45.513 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:35:45.613 --> 00:35:47.414 position:19% line:89% align:start
