00:35:47.515 --> 00:35:48.683 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, nice chat.

00:35:49.884 --> 00:35:51.686 position:21% line:83% align:start
I just wish we could
have more time.

00:35:56.758 --> 00:35:57.759 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
 <i>Why was I even born?</i>

00:35:59.393 --> 00:36:01.194 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's all I ever</i>
 <i>asked myself back then.</i>

00:36:02.930 --> 00:36:05.298 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>You know, I really believed</i>
 <i>that I would get better.</i>

00:36:06.801 --> 00:36:08.703 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Maybe that's why I</i>
 <i>lasted till spring.</i>

00:36:08.803 --> 00:36:10.705 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Aoi cries]

00:36:10.805 --> 00:36:12.640 position:19% line:89% align:start
I died six months ago.

00:36:12.740 --> 00:36:13.841 position:19% line:89% align:start
You still that torn up?

00:36:15.043 --> 00:36:17.411 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Everything is gonna work</i>
 <i>out for the two of you.</i>

00:36:19.312 --> 00:36:20.782 position:21% line:89% align:start
