00:36:20.882 --> 00:36:21.949 position:24% line:89% align:start
but I guarantee it.

00:36:23.751 --> 00:36:24.786 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tomoya,</i>

00:36:26.319 --> 00:36:26.954 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>Aoi,</i>

00:36:28.589 --> 00:36:30.223 position:19% line:89% align:start
go live your best life.

00:36:39.600 --> 00:36:42.436 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Aoi crying quietly]

00:36:52.446 --> 00:36:53.346 position:30% line:89% align:start
Let's go home.

00:36:57.051 --> 00:36:57.885 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:36:59.453 --> 00:37:01.723 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

